{"tid":1942384,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"WHO：美國或成為下一個武漢肺炎的疫情「震央」","createTime":"2020-03-25T04:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T13:57:09.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b94fcc07f8ed22ddcb4940d90f4c2f5cf72e0ed2","tid":1942384,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情蔓延全球，美國疫情加劇，約翰斯&middot;霍普金斯大學的數據顯示，美國在週二（24日）單日確診數字超過 1 萬人，累計達 5 萬多人感染，死亡人數近 8 百人。其中以紐約情況最為嚴峻，總確診人數高達 2 萬 5 千人，佔全國確診數字的一半。新澤西州、加州及華盛頓確診數字亦不斷遞增，確診人數共超過 2,000 人。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線電視新聞網（CNN）引述世界衛生組織發言人 Margaret Harris 指，繼歐洲之後，美國確診人數不斷攀升，全球過去 24 小時的新增確診個案，有 85% 來自歐洲及美國。她認為美國有可能成為下一個武漢肺炎的全球疫情震央。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/武漢肺炎-美國再新增逾萬人確診-累計破-5-萬宗-航母羅斯福號-3-海軍感染/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%86%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%BE%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88%E7%A0%B4-5-%E8%90%AC%E5%AE%97-%E8%88%AA%E6%AF%8D%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%A6%8F%E8%99%9F-3-%E6%B5%B7%E8%BB%8D%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%2F&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn5ktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=0e203683\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%86%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%BE%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E7%B4%AF%E8%A8%88%E7%A0%B4-5-%E8%90%AC%E5%AE%97-%E8%88%AA%E6%AF%8D%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%A6%8F%E8%99%9F-3-%E6%B5%B7%E8%BB%8D%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%2F&h=939ffd82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/武漢肺炎-美國再新增逾萬人確診-累計破-5-萬宗-航母羅斯福號-3-海軍感染/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c870480a71505e3393f589261811b565bbf8535","tid":1942384,"uid":35820,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T04:49:27.000Z","msg":"每次都講埋啲發生咗嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.